dictionary.title: EMA
dictionary.description: The moving average of the stock prices that places greater weight and significance on the recent prices. EMA tends to react faster to the recent price fluctuations than SMA

dictionary.title: SMA
dictionary.description: Simple Moving average of the stock prices

dictionary.title: Volume Weighted Average Price
dictionary.description: Volume Weighted Average Price(VWAP) is simply an average price of a security over a time period. So, "120 days VWAP" means 120 days average price.
